A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Matt Brinson; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, Matt Brinson has diligently and conscientiously devoted innumerable hours of
3 his time, talents, and energy toward the betterment of his community and state, as evidenced
4 dramatically by his superlative leadership as part of the Planters Electric Membership
5 Corporation (EMC); and
6 WHEREAS, he began his 48-year tenure as a warehouse clerk and progressed through
7 positions such as plant accountant, manager of administrative services, and assistant manager
8 before assuming the role of general manager on February 1, 1999, leading the cooperative
9 in serving consumers across seven counties in Southeast Georgia; and
10 WHEREAS, he has contributed significantly to the cooperative sector through his service on
11 the Go Energy Financial Credit Union Board, the Smarr EMC Board, and the Georgia
12 Energy Cooperative Board; and
13 WHEREAS, he further exemplified his dedication to the rural electric industry by serving
14 as president of the Georgia Rural Electric Managers' Association in 2011; and
